{"tid":1624620,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[Twitter戰線] 建議立即係Twitter表達香港人暫時唔支持臨時政府","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:16:26.000Z","uid":49781,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef0c86c22f7cb7640c9cfb03e588b0dcc08a862","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我明白大家嘅心好想獨立，不過為咗順利通過香港人權與民主法案，我哋應該要按部就班，係目前局勢先專注五大(或六大)訴求同捍衛民主、人權、自由等口號，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果唔係西方國家係冇藉口介入香港事務</span></strong>。可能有啲人會話唔使理外國點諗，其實呢個諗法好錯，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇咗西方、日本等國家支持我哋贏嘅機會好微</span></strong>，為咗減少不穩定因素，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請大家暫時停止討論香港臨時政府，並且將之前嘅核彈例如學生食實彈、印尼記者失明等發酵！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter記得@Solomon、@Pelosi同埋加上適當嘅Tag"},{"pid":"6fc8167fb2db55137c2f6a5a5f019d4081135df0","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"自推20<br />\n<br />\n1/20"},{"pid":"69e284e30101b0ffbe02eb374e28c3147d3e7360","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"自推20<br />\n<br />\n2/20"},{"pid":"7ed10c07d73df064c635129124a4cc8204d7563b","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"自推20<br />\n<br />\n3/20"},{"pid":"24aa492c16c684da5843f5f4d1e749089c6d2164","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:39.000Z","msg":"自推20<br />\n<br />\n4/20"},{"pid":"c9b0eb4fdf75340510c85cc05083e73df3c220f2","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"自推20<br />\n<br />\n5/20"},{"pid":"b32deb576b56de648df2897c30e70e6a58d8ac4e","tid":1624620,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"自推20<br />\n<br />\n6/20"},{"pid":"06057